    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just what people say to keep things going, right? to keep the cycle moving. but there's no actual reason for it. i look at the world and i just see a cold, dark void. everything is just temporary and then it's gone. it's not like there's some light at the end of the tunnel or anything. it's just more darkness.",
